Thu Apr 29 18:59:55 UTC 2021 - Ferdinand Thiessen <rpm@fthiessen.de>

- Update to version 7.16
  * Added code to allow the ``TEXTDOMAINDIR`` environment variable
    to specify where compiled translations are located.
  * Added an application metadata file that conforms to the
    AppStream 0.12 specification.
  * Updated the German translation
- Update to version 7.15
  * Changed the default location where game files are saved
    from `~/.trader` to `~/.local/share/trader`, so as to follow
    the `XDG Base Directory Specification`
  * If set to an absolute path, the ``XDG_DATA_HOME`` environment
    variable will override this location.
  * If the `~/.trader` directory is already present, it will
    continue to be used.
  * Updated the Russian translation

